# Baked build channel — "production" | "development". Leave unset for `bun run dev` (development:
# chat/profile/run registered). Builds MUST set it (the build's missing-var guard rejects an unset
# value); set INFLEXA_BUILD_CHANNEL=production to omit the dev commands from the binary. scripts/build.ts
# also --defines NODE_ENV from this value, so bundled dependencies compile in the same mode.
# INFLEXA_BUILD_CHANNEL=production
